original_title: AVP The Monster Hydro Cup Day 2-1: Men’s Semi-Final 1 - Dalhausser and Lucena vs Tr. Crabb and Bourne
overview: Pro beach volleyball returns with the AVP Champions Cup Series from Long Beach, California. Three tournaments, three teams per gender crowned champions, only ONE team per gender with the ultimate reward of the Champions Cup.
